					"value": "passive"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>60 feet, @Check[will|dc:17|traits:auditory,mental]. </p><p>Creatures who starts their turn inside the aura must attempt at a Will save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> the creature is unaffected and immune for 24h</p><p><strong>Success</strong> the creature is unaffected.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> the creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied 2} until the end of their next turn.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> the creature is Stupefied 2 and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.yblD8fOR1J8rDwEQ]{Confused} until the start of their next turn.</p>",
