			"name": "Madness",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "passive"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>Whenever a creature attempts to targets the allip with a spells that controls the mind of other creatures (like @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.aIHY2DArKFweIrpf]{Command} or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.OsOhx3TGIZ7AhD0P]{Dominate}) must attempt at a @Check[will|dc:17] save. If they fails they become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied 1} and their spell is counteracted. If they critically fails they become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied 2} instead.</p>",
