			"name": "Touch of Insanity",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "passive"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>Whenever a creature is hit or critically hit by an allip's maddening touch Strike, they must attempt at a @Check[will|dc:17] save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> Target creature is unaffected and immune for 24 hours.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> Target creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied 1}.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> the creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied 2} and takes @Damage[1d8[mental,persistent]] damage.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> as failure, but the creature takes @Damage[2d8[mental,persistent]] damage.</p>",
